race.comment: MAKE A CALL (6) grows a leg for hoop Maloney who has three wins from just four steers and is yet to miss a quinella spot in three attempts over this track and trip. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a major role in the finish. BRAVE CALL (9) resumes here but has a solid fresh record with a win and two placings from four starts. Gets 2kg off with the claim and maps well from gate four. Can run a race first-up. CHILLAXING (10) is one from one around this circuit and has tuned up for this with a recent easy trial. Include from the favourable draw. The well-related CAVALRY MAN (2) (half to G2 winner Positive Peace) has been thereabouts in all five runs this campaign and is a must for the multiples.
